sentences: Akwuba Charles Ugochukwu (born November 4, 1989), professionally known as DJ Coublon, is a Nigerian record producer and sound engineer.
Born on November 4, 1989, he began his interest in music at the age of 7.
In 2013 he moved to Lagos where he met other artists like Iyanya and Kiss Daniel.
He was signed onto Made Men Music Group between September 2014 to 2016.
